How to make the snapshots:
    
    * Use konsole, with the font Terminus, size 23
    * For the colors, choose Dark Pastels (Settings, Manage, Edit, Appareance)
    * With ksnapshot, choose the region you want to snapshot
    * As much as possible, the width of the snapshot should be 1062
    * Include the snapshot in your slide with :
        \includegraphics[scale=0.35]{snapshot.png}
